FBIS3-12864 "drnes044_n_94006" FBIS-NES-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 LEBANON Officials Discuss Developments in Church Bombing French Diplomat Denounces Bombing NC0103125194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon in Arabic 1145 GMT 1 Mar 94 NC0103125194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Denis Barbet, second counselor at the French Embassy, has denounced the explosion at the Maronite church. He said it is up to the Lebanese authorities to determine the circumstances and reasons behind the incident. The French official was speaking after a visit to the Bustrus Palace, where he handed the Foreign Ministry's secretary general a message from French Foreign Minister Alain Juppe to Minister Faris Buwayz. He declined to reveal the content of the message, leaving this up to Buwayz.
